The session id used in telemetry for the current session. This will return %s if telemetry is disabled. In general, this key is used to track individual sessions. If needed, this can be provided to the maintainers to associate your data with you. If you wish for your telemetry data to remain anonymous, do not provide this key to the maintainers. (People without access to the telemetry system cannot do anything with the key anyways.)
